<!-- fifth -->

<div  class="  mt-4 d-flex justify-center justify-evenly" >

<div>
    <h1><span>Salt'n Pepper</span> Restaurant</h1>
    <p class="text-grey">
       The Salt’n Pepper Restaurants at Mall and Liberty Market Lahore, are considered to be the first<br>proper family style restaurants in the food industry of Pakistan. These restaurants pride <br>themselves for being symbolized as an eatery with a customer loyalty spanning over three generations. <br>As a restaurant model, these have inspired the set-up of numerous other restaurants across Pakistan.</p>
</div>

